Then tonight at six,

571
00:23:41,460 --> 00:23:44,860
I will await you all at the Grand Hotel.

572
00:23:45,100 --> 00:23:45,820
Thank you, Mr. Gao.

573
00:23:45,820 --> 00:23:47,260
Farewell.

574
00:23:47,300 --> 00:23:48,180
Take care.

575
00:23:48,860 --> 00:23:49,620
Mr. Chen, I can see myself out.

576
00:23:49,620 --> 00:23:50,380
Don't trouble yourself.

577
00:24:05,780 --> 00:24:07,060
When we were back in Qizhou,

578
00:24:07,620 --> 00:24:09,100
you said you'd take me
to the Grand Hotel

579
00:24:09,100 --> 00:24:10,020
so I could see what it's all about.

580
00:24:11,220 --> 00:24:12,620
I didn't expect it
to actually come true.

581
00:24:14,060 --> 00:24:15,060
They say

582
00:24:15,820 --> 00:24:17,140
one meal there

583
00:24:18,060 --> 00:24:20,420
costs more than
a family's yearly budget.

584
00:24:21,620 --> 00:24:22,540
I also heard

585
00:24:23,060 --> 00:24:24,580
only foreigners stay there.

586
00:24:27,140 --> 00:24:27,900
What's wrong?

587
00:24:32,740 --> 00:24:33,500
What's on your mind?

588
00:24:35,300 --> 00:24:36,220
I was just thinking

589
00:24:37,460 --> 00:24:39,300
Shouyuan Apothecary
is such a giant in the business.

590
00:24:40,100 --> 00:24:41,660
Compared to them,

591
00:24:42,180 --> 00:24:43,700
we're barely a speck.

592
00:24:45,020 --> 00:24:46,180
Maybe we should just forget it.

593
00:24:50,340 --> 00:24:52,460
If Shouyuan Apothecary managed

594
00:24:52,460 --> 00:24:53,500
to grow their business that big,

595
00:24:53,780 --> 00:24:56,660
it means they're not fools, right?

596
00:24:58,220 --> 00:25:00,780
They know we're not a big operation,

597
00:25:01,100 --> 00:25:02,580
yet they still came to us
for a partnership.

598
00:25:02,860 --> 00:25:05,820
They must see something special in us.

599
00:25:06,660 --> 00:25:08,300
If they value us this much,

600
00:25:08,580 --> 00:25:10,660
then we've no reason to doubt ourselves.

601
00:25:12,100 --> 00:25:13,300
That's true,

602
00:25:14,380 --> 00:25:15,380
but deep down,

603
00:25:16,300 --> 00:25:17,660
I still feel uneasy.

604
00:25:19,620 --> 00:25:20,700
Do you think

605
00:25:21,100 --> 00:25:23,420
it's because the owner
of Shouyuan Apothecary is Xia Yuan

606
00:25:24,220 --> 00:25:25,540
that you're feeling uneasy?

607
00:25:33,260 --> 00:25:34,020
Dashun,

608
00:25:35,380 --> 00:25:37,740
since I chose to marry you then,

609
00:25:39,180 --> 00:25:41,220
it means I've made up my mind.

610
00:25:41,300 --> 00:25:42,580
You're the one I chose for this life.

611
00:25:44,860 --> 00:25:45,660
Shaohua.

612
00:25:46,700 --> 00:25:47,420
Don't worry,

613
00:25:48,340 --> 00:25:50,700
only you and the Chen family.

614
00:25:51,540 --> 00:25:53,260
All I care about now

615
00:25:53,260 --> 00:25:54,620
is making our family business

616
00:25:54,620 --> 00:25:55,900
thrive.

617
00:25:58,620 --> 00:25:59,340
I'm sorry.

618
00:26:00,260 --> 00:26:01,500
I let my emotions get the better of me.

619
00:26:03,220 --> 00:26:04,300
Go get changed.

620
00:26:05,380 --> 00:26:05,900
Okay.

621
00:26:06,500 --> 00:26:09,300
Get me the black iron-thread jacket.

622
00:26:10,100 --> 00:26:11,420
What took you so long?

623
00:26:13,900 --> 00:26:14,980
That's the one.

624
00:26:21,220 --> 00:26:24,620
Grand Hotel. Awsome.

625
00:26:26,140 --> 00:26:27,100
I just saw it

626
00:26:27,100 --> 00:26:28,980
from afar.

627
00:26:28,980 --> 00:26:30,780
I didn't even dare to walk closer.

628
00:26:32,100 --> 00:26:33,260
Don't worry.

629
00:26:33,900 --> 00:26:36,540
Once this deal
with Shouyuan Apothecary goes through,

630
00:26:37,820 --> 00:26:38,660
and we start making money,

631
00:26:39,740 --> 00:26:41,420
I'll take you there
so you can check it out for yourself.

632
00:26:41,980 --> 00:26:42,700
No.

633
00:26:42,860 --> 00:26:43,900
Is the collar okay?

634
00:26:43,900 --> 00:26:45,340
I'm not going.

635
00:26:46,900 --> 00:26:48,100
We don't need to splurge on that.

636
00:26:48,100 --> 00:26:49,580
I heard there are many foreigners.

637
00:26:49,740 --> 00:26:51,300
I'd save that money instead.

638
00:26:51,540 --> 00:26:54,340
You're always pinching pennies.

639
00:26:54,380 --> 00:26:55,060
Is that all you know?

640
00:26:55,060 --> 00:26:56,780
Father, the carriage is here.

641
00:26:57,260 --> 00:26:57,900
Father.

642
00:26:57,900 --> 00:26:58,460
Mother.

643
00:27:00,460 --> 00:27:01,700
Very good.

644
00:27:01,860 --> 00:27:03,380
Wearing something that flashy,

645
00:27:03,380 --> 00:27:04,780
don't you think people might talk?

646
00:27:05,220 --> 00:27:05,780
Mother...

647
00:27:05,780 --> 00:27:08,100
That's nonsense.

648
00:27:09,180 --> 00:27:10,860
When she looks good,

649
00:27:10,980 --> 00:27:13,660
it makes the whole family
look good. Got it?

650
00:27:16,500 --> 00:27:17,020
Let's go.

651
00:27:17,060 --> 00:27:17,660
Wait.

652
00:27:28,020 --> 00:27:29,460
Put these on.

653
00:27:32,140 --> 00:27:32,860
Take them.

654
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:35,580
Don't let anyone think less of us.

655
00:27:37,900 --> 00:27:38,620
Thank you, Mother.

656
00:27:38,860 --> 00:27:39,780
Don't lose them.

657
00:27:39,780 --> 00:27:41,500
You have to give them back.

658
00:27:41,500 --> 00:27:43,700
Are you going to let her
wear them or not?

659
00:27:44,140 --> 00:27:44,700
Yes.

660
00:27:44,900 --> 00:27:45,620
So annoying.

661
00:27:45,780 --> 00:27:46,620
Let's go.

662
00:27:46,860 --> 00:27:47,500
Mother, we're leaving.

663
00:27:47,500 --> 00:27:48,180
Bye, Mother.

664
00:28:13,860 --> 00:28:14,660
Let's go.

665
00:28:52,020 --> 00:28:52,820
Mr. Chen,

666
00:28:53,340 --> 00:28:54,860
Mr. and Mrs. Chen Junior.

667
00:28:55,060 --> 00:28:55,540
Mr. Gao.

668
00:28:55,580 --> 00:28:56,500
Apologies for not coming out
to meet you.

669
00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:57,940
This way, please.

670
00:28:57,940 --> 00:28:58,900
Please.

671
00:28:58,900 --> 00:28:59,700
After you.

672
00:28:59,700 --> 00:29:00,660
Come, Mr. Chen Junior.

673
00:29:01,620 --> 00:29:02,580
Mr. Chen.

674
00:29:04,740 --> 00:29:05,340
This way.

675
00:29:05,340 --> 00:29:05,740
Okay.

676
00:29:07,860 --> 00:29:09,540
I meant to come down and welcome you.

677
00:29:09,580 --> 00:29:11,300
I'm so sorry I didn't make it.

678
00:29:11,300 --> 00:29:12,180
Come on.

679
00:29:12,420 --> 00:29:13,660
This way, please.

680
00:29:15,780 --> 00:29:16,380
Please.

681
00:29:31,300 --> 00:29:32,580
I'm truly sorry.

682
00:29:33,020 --> 00:29:35,420
Our head manager Mr. Xu

683
00:29:35,980 --> 00:29:37,460
was supposed to come today.

684
00:29:38,220 --> 00:29:39,100
But unfortunately,

685
00:29:39,380 --> 00:29:40,860
Mr. Yan, the Military Governor
of Shanxi,

686
00:29:40,980 --> 00:29:43,380
appointed the largest
local pharmaceutical trader

687
00:29:43,500 --> 00:29:44,860
to lead a procurement delegation

688
00:29:44,900 --> 00:29:46,940
to Peking to purchase
medicinal materials.

689
00:29:47,460 --> 00:29:48,340
So Mr. Xu

690
00:29:48,420 --> 00:29:49,980
rushed over to entertain them.

691
00:29:50,100 --> 00:29:50,900
Since it's just me tonight,

692
00:29:51,820 --> 00:29:55,140
I'll do my best to host your family.

693
00:29:55,740 --> 00:29:57,860
Mr. Gao, thank you.

694
00:29:57,980 --> 00:29:59,340
You're too kind.

695
00:30:00,180 --> 00:30:00,860
Please dig in.

696
00:30:02,420 --> 00:30:05,740
The Taigu traders in Shanxi
are no small players.

697
00:30:05,780 --> 00:30:07,380
Why would they come all the way
to Peking

698
00:30:07,620 --> 00:30:09,220
instead of sourcing locally?

699
00:30:11,580 --> 00:30:12,460
Ma'am,

700
00:30:12,740 --> 00:30:14,260
you may not know.

701
00:30:14,500 --> 00:30:17,380
Taigu's traders are led
by the Guang Trade Guild,

702
00:30:17,580 --> 00:30:19,420
known for premium tonics.

703
00:30:19,900 --> 00:30:21,740
But this time,

704
00:30:21,980 --> 00:30:23,220
they came to Peking

705
00:30:23,780 --> 00:30:26,820
for battlefield medical supplies.

706
00:30:27,500 --> 00:30:28,780
Is there going to be a war?

707
00:30:29,220 --> 00:30:32,140
A military government
has taken hold in Guangdong.

708
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:33,620
The North-South conflict

709
00:30:35,100 --> 00:30:36,060
is bound

710
00:30:37,020 --> 00:30:38,220
to happen.

711
00:30:39,380 --> 00:30:42,300
It's the common folk who'll suffer.

712
00:30:44,020 --> 00:30:45,780
Mr. Chen Junior, your compassion

713
00:30:46,180 --> 00:30:47,540
is truly something to be admired.

714
00:30:47,620 --> 00:30:50,900
Here, I'll drink a toast to you.

715
00:30:50,900 --> 00:30:52,100
Mr. Gao, you flatter me.

716
00:30:52,500 --> 00:30:53,460
Come on.

717
00:30:53,460 --> 00:30:54,340
I'd like to make a toast, too.

718
00:30:55,100 --> 00:30:56,620
May peace prevail
throughout the land soon,

719
00:30:56,900 --> 00:30:58,700
and may the common people
live in stable times.

720
00:30:59,540 --> 00:31:01,780
Truly a match made in heaven.

721
00:31:01,900 --> 00:31:03,140
Come on.

722
00:31:04,020 --> 00:31:04,500
Come.

723
00:31:09,860 --> 00:31:11,740
The war may be raging,

724
00:31:12,300 --> 00:31:14,180
but business still has to go on.

725
00:31:15,860 --> 00:31:17,460
This military supply order

726
00:31:17,660 --> 00:31:21,220
must be at least 30,000 silver dollars,
right?

727
00:31:22,780 --> 00:31:23,540
Approximately.

728
00:31:25,620 --> 00:31:27,460
With Shouyuan Apothecary making a move,

729
00:31:28,380 --> 00:31:31,060
it's definitely a sure thing.

730
00:31:32,340 --> 00:31:33,060
Mr. Chen,

731
00:31:33,220 --> 00:31:34,340
you flatter us.

732
00:31:35,180 --> 00:31:36,620
To be honest,

733
00:31:36,820 --> 00:31:40,100
the top ten apothecaries in China

734
00:31:41,100 --> 00:31:43,020
are all eyeing this juicy piece of meat.

735
00:31:43,380 --> 00:31:44,660
We

736
00:31:46,860 --> 00:31:48,700
might not necessarily
be able to secure it.

737
00:31:50,740 --> 00:31:51,700
Mr. Gao,

738
00:31:52,300 --> 00:31:54,620
if even you cannot secure this order,

739
00:31:55,180 --> 00:31:55,980
I'm afraid

740
00:31:56,420 --> 00:31:57,220
others

741
00:31:58,740 --> 00:32:00,140
will be even less likely to.

742
00:32:00,580 --> 00:32:01,820
I wouldn't be so sure about that.

743
00:32:01,900 --> 00:32:02,940
Well,

744
00:32:03,420 --> 00:32:07,220
congratulations in advance.

745
00:32:07,900 --> 00:32:08,620
Mr. Gao.

746
00:32:09,540 --> 00:32:12,140
I'll take your words

747
00:32:12,300 --> 00:32:13,380
as a blessing.

748
00:32:14,060 --> 00:32:14,940
Thanks.

749
00:32:19,980 --> 00:32:21,060
Have a seat.

750
00:32:22,020 --> 00:32:23,580
Enough business for now.

751
00:32:24,580 --> 00:32:25,380
Please dig in.

752
00:32:26,140 --> 00:32:26,940
Okay.

753
00:32:26,980 --> 00:32:27,740
Please.

754
00:32:30,100 --> 00:32:31,340
Come on, please.

755
00:32:37,020 --> 00:32:37,700
Mr. Chen,

756
00:32:38,540 --> 00:32:40,620
I'll prepare the cooperation agreement

757
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:43,140
as discussed

758
00:32:43,140 --> 00:32:44,140
and let you review it.

759
00:32:44,140 --> 00:32:44,660
Please.

760
00:32:47,060 --> 00:32:48,260
Are you okay?

761
00:32:48,460 --> 00:32:49,340
I'm fine.

762
00:32:50,340 --> 00:32:50,940
Are you alright?

763
00:32:51,100 --> 00:32:51,780
Mr. Xu,

764
00:32:52,820 --> 00:32:54,460
you really didn't have to
go to such expense.

765
00:32:54,460 --> 00:32:55,420
Don't mention it.

766
00:32:55,540 --> 00:32:57,580
We're honored to have you.

767
00:32:57,860 --> 00:32:58,620
Okay.

768
00:32:58,660 --> 00:32:59,780
Thanks in advance.

769
00:32:59,780 --> 00:33:00,540
Okay.

770
00:33:02,580 --> 00:33:03,300
Easy.

771
00:33:04,700 --> 00:33:06,020
Alright, see you around.

772
00:33:07,060 --> 00:33:08,580
Take him to the Peking Hotel.

773
00:33:08,580 --> 00:33:09,100
Okay.

774
00:33:09,100 --> 00:33:10,740
Father, the carriage is here.

775
00:33:11,820 --> 00:33:12,500
Mr. Gao,

776
00:33:12,620 --> 00:33:13,740
I'll take my leave.

777
00:33:13,740 --> 00:33:15,300
Mr. Chen, take care.

778
00:33:15,540 --> 00:33:16,980
Farewell. Okay.

779
00:33:17,100 --> 00:33:18,780
Ma'am, please.

780
00:33:18,980 --> 00:33:19,420
Okay.

781
00:33:29,020 --> 00:33:31,540
A military medical supply order
of 30,000 silver dollars.

782
00:33:32,820 --> 00:33:33,900
This could easily bring in

783
00:33:35,900 --> 00:33:38,060
over 10,000 in profit.

784
00:33:38,820 --> 00:33:40,660
Shouyuan Apothecary
holds serious influence.

785
00:33:41,020 --> 00:33:43,180
They have raw medicinal material outlets
in every key production region.

786
00:33:43,460 --> 00:33:44,500
I'm afraid it's more than that.

787
00:33:47,140 --> 00:33:49,420
What if we do it instead?

788
00:33:50,580 --> 00:33:51,420
What are you thinking?

789
00:33:53,180 --> 00:33:54,260
Doing business.

790
00:33:55,660 --> 00:33:56,460
We don't have

791
00:33:56,460 --> 00:33:58,220
Shouyuan's pricing edge,

792
00:33:58,500 --> 00:33:59,540
but we should still be able

793
00:33:59,860 --> 00:34:01,540
to pull in 5,000 or more.

794
00:34:02,900 --> 00:34:04,060
How could such an order

795
00:34:04,060 --> 00:34:05,220
fall into our hands?

796
00:34:07,140 --> 00:34:08,060
Why not?

797
00:34:09,300 --> 00:34:10,740
Didn't you hear Mr. Gao say?

798
00:34:11,180 --> 00:34:13,700
The top ten apothecaries in China
are all eyeing it.

799
00:34:14,420 --> 00:34:15,020
Let's not dwell on it.

800
00:34:15,020 --> 00:34:16,180
We've got a small business to run,

801
00:34:16,180 --> 00:34:17,860
and we'll do it right.

802
00:34:21,620 --> 00:34:23,020
We've got to keep
the small business going,

803
00:34:23,140 --> 00:34:24,500
but we should also think
about the bigger opportunities.

804
00:34:25,500 --> 00:34:27,220
But some things are pointless
to think about.

805
00:34:28,380 --> 00:34:29,140
Dashun,

806
00:34:29,620 --> 00:34:31,780
I actually think we can try.

807
00:34:34,780 --> 00:34:35,740
You sure you're okay?

808
00:34:36,420 --> 00:34:37,540
What if it works?

809
00:34:38,140 --> 00:34:39,020
Impossible.

810
00:34:42,220 --> 00:34:42,940
Look,

811
00:34:43,660 --> 00:34:44,660
Xuan isn't smiling.

812
00:34:44,740 --> 00:34:45,900
Even she thinks you're fantasizing.

813
00:34:48,530 --> 00:34:57,480
[Peking Hotel]

814
00:34:57,540 --> 00:34:58,140
Thank you.

815
00:35:00,800 --> 00:35:02,280
[Peking Hotel]

816
00:35:06,820 --> 00:35:07,460
Excuse me.

817
00:35:07,780 --> 00:35:09,700
I am Chu Shaohua from Chen's Apothecary.

818
00:35:10,020 --> 00:35:10,860
I've come to visit

819
00:35:10,860 --> 00:35:12,740
the Procurement Commissioner
of Mr. Yan of Shanxi.

820
00:35:13,060 --> 00:35:14,660
Please announce my arrival.

821
00:35:14,940 --> 00:35:15,900
Mr. Xu has given orders

822
00:35:16,140 --> 00:35:17,220
that no one is to be announced.

823
00:35:18,820 --> 00:35:20,620
Sir, please help me.

824
00:35:21,100 --> 00:35:22,140
I can't.

825
00:35:22,340 --> 00:35:23,180
Look at this crowd.

826
00:35:23,180 --> 00:35:24,620
Everyone's here for him.

827
00:35:24,900 --> 00:35:26,100
Find a spot and wait.

828
00:35:27,100 --> 00:35:27,740
Thank you.

829
00:35:27,940 --> 00:35:29,500
Everyone in Peking knows

830
00:35:29,500 --> 00:35:30,940
your Hanchun Apothecary.

831
00:35:31,740 --> 00:35:33,180
You're giving me too much credit.

832
00:35:33,180 --> 00:35:34,740
Compared to your Qingyu Apothecary,

833
00:35:34,820 --> 00:35:35,900
we still have a long way to go.

834
00:35:36,500 --> 00:35:37,580
You flatter me.

835
00:35:37,780 --> 00:35:39,980
Who else has come too?

836
00:35:40,700 --> 00:35:41,900
Mr. Tian is also here.

837
00:35:42,220 --> 00:35:43,220
Which Mr. Tian?

838
00:35:43,540 --> 00:35:46,060
Mr. Tian from Tian's Apothecary
in Shanghai.

839
00:35:47,300 --> 00:35:49,940
Even Tian's Apothecary is here?

840
00:35:50,460 --> 00:35:52,140
I'm afraid we have no hope.

841
00:35:52,620 --> 00:35:53,820
The Tians

842
00:35:54,060 --> 00:35:55,260
have built an empire,

843
00:35:55,260 --> 00:35:56,100
and they're still chasing scraps
from folks like us.

844
00:35:56,100 --> 00:35:57,500
Mr. Xu is here.

845
00:35:57,500 --> 00:35:58,180
Mr. Xu!

846
00:35:58,460 --> 00:35:59,060
Where is he?

847
00:35:59,060 --> 00:35:59,860
I am from Qingyu Apothecary.

848
00:35:59,860 --> 00:36:01,460
- Mr. Xu!
- Mr. Xu!

849
00:36:01,460 --> 00:36:02,580
- I'm from Qingyu Apothecary!
- Mr. Xu!

850
00:36:02,860 --> 00:36:05,300
- Mr. Xu!
- Mr. Xu!

851
00:36:05,700 --> 00:36:07,140
- Mr. Xu!
- Mr. Xu!

852
00:36:07,740 --> 00:36:08,620
Mr. Xu!

853
00:36:08,620 --> 00:36:10,180
I'm from Qingyu Apothecary!

854
00:36:10,340 --> 00:36:11,940
Mr. Xu, over here!

855
00:36:11,940 --> 00:36:13,060
