856
00:36:35,700 --> 00:36:36,980
Who do you think you are?

857
00:36:37,420 --> 00:36:38,580
You think you're somebody?

858
00:36:39,300 --> 00:36:40,300
Listen up.

859
00:36:40,300 --> 00:36:42,580
I'm the one in charge here!

860
00:36:42,580 --> 00:36:44,980
I call the shots
in the Logistics Department!

861
00:36:45,420 --> 00:36:46,220
You think I'm bluffing?

862
00:36:46,500 --> 00:36:47,900
One word from me

863
00:36:47,980 --> 00:36:49,020
