865
00:36:51,300 --> 00:36:51,940
Do it, I dare you!

866
00:36:51,940 --> 00:36:52,380
Why wouldn't I dare?

867
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:53,300
Mr. Lan, let's just drop it.

868
00:36:53,300 --> 00:36:54,780
Don't take me for a pushover!

869
00:36:55,060 --> 00:36:57,220
