885
00:37:37,340 --> 00:37:38,300
How about

886
00:37:39,620 --> 00:37:40,780
I take you to Shanxi?

887
00:37:41,420 --> 00:37:43,300
Good food, soft beds,

888
00:37:43,300 --> 00:37:45,500
