915
00:38:59,580 --> 00:39:01,180
That's Mr. Shang, an adjutant.

916
00:39:02,380 --> 00:39:03,540
He's a good person, though.

917
00:39:04,580 --> 00:39:06,500
But in front of those two,

918
00:39:06,500 --> 00:39:07,820
