921
00:39:18,820 --> 00:39:20,300
Pick up something tasty for your mother.

922
00:39:20,740 --> 00:39:21,300
Hua.

923
00:39:22,140 --> 00:39:23,180
You

924
00:39:23,500 --> 00:39:24,740
cleaned me up,

925
00:39:25,180 --> 00:39:26,140
took care of my wounds,

926
00:39:26,460 --> 00:39:28,060
and treated me
to all kinds of good things.

927
00:39:28,500 --> 00:39:30,140
How could I possibly take your money?

928
00:39:30,140 --> 00:39:30,980
Just take it.

929
00:39:31,300 --> 00:39:33,020
I'll probably be bothering you a lot.

930
00:39:34,860 --> 00:39:35,860
Thank you.

931
00:39:36,100 --> 00:39:36,900
Go ahead.

932
00:39:37,260 --> 00:39:38,260
There's still some shaomai left.

933
00:39:38,540 --> 00:39:39,700
Tell me if you need more.

934
00:39:43,100 --> 00:39:43,940
Dashun.

935
00:39:44,660 --> 00:39:45,580
Where have you been?

936
00:39:47,660 --> 00:39:48,740
Mr. Gao is here?

937
00:39:49,420 --> 00:39:50,460
He's been here for quite a while.

938
00:39:50,500 --> 00:39:52,100
He's discussing
the cooperation agreement with Father.

939
00:39:52,100 --> 00:39:54,700
I completely understand your concerns.

940
00:39:55,420 --> 00:39:57,060
I'll check in with Mr. Xia,

941
00:39:57,060 --> 00:39:58,100
and we'll give it some more thought.

942
00:39:58,780 --> 00:39:59,500
Of course,

943
00:39:59,980 --> 00:40:01,900
if you change your mind,

944
00:40:02,260 --> 00:40:04,620
I'll await your presence at any time.

945
00:40:05,540 --> 00:40:06,380
Mr. Gao.

946
00:40:07,220 --> 00:40:07,900
I appreciate it.

947
00:40:09,140 --> 00:40:09,820
Mr. Gao.

948
00:40:11,500 --> 00:40:12,660
Ma'am, you're back.

949
