isn't going to go through.

976
00:41:24,420 --> 00:41:25,220
Why?

977
00:41:26,020 --> 00:41:29,580
They want us to share
the secret formula of Yurong Powder.

978
00:41:31,020 --> 00:41:32,180
For every box sold,

979
00:41:33,260 --> 00:41:38,420
