a forty-sixty profit split.

986
00:41:54,620 --> 00:41:56,100
How could I possibly agree to that?

987
00:41:57,300 --> 00:42:00,100
They're throwing their weight around.

988
00:42:01,780 --> 00:42:02,420
Father,

989
00:42:03,500 --> 00:42:04,660
I actually think

990
00:42:05,380 --> 00:42:07,060
